      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING HAGEN (4) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when third beaten 6 lengths (30.92). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can measure up this time. SIMPLICITY MAGIC (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (30.14) at Wentworth Park behind Zipping Chetty in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Expected to feature. LAST SHOT RIPPER (5) ran a good time (30.60) when placing three back at this track but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing sixth (31.03) at this track. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Rates a winning chance on best. MESSY AND UNTIDY (2) can fill a top-three spot.",
